<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">د ن ق:</span> <span class="c2">(الدَّانَقُ)</span> بِفَتْحِ النُّونِ وَكَسْرِهَا سُدْسُ الدِّرْهَمِ وَ <span class="c2">(الْمُدَنِّقُ)</span> الْمُسْتَقْصِي.<span class="c5"> قَالَ الْحَسَنُ:</span> لَا <span class="c2">(تُدَنِّقُوا)</span> <span class="c2">(فَيُدَنَّقَ)</span> عَلَيْكُمْ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>